 today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"components"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are not defined yet."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"They can be seen as an high level of usage with functional meanings."}]}}}